1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a region regression-based multi-stage class-agnostic detection pipeline for object detection, which is a common problem in computer vision.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper utilizes deep learning techniques for region regression and proposes a novel network architecture.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of existing detection algorithms using deep learning techniques.
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper proposes a neural network architecture for object detection.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with object detection in images, which is a common multimedia application.
